{"tid":1133371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港科大女生涉趁同屋主外遊虐貓 騰訊：若屬實終止實習工作","createTime":"2019-05-01T04:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T08:12:54.000Z","uid":56881,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c2bff4b937fe7d89c31299ae1354181752443f","tid":1133371,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%89%E8%B6%81%E5%90%8C%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%A4%96%E9%81%8A%E8%99%90%E8%B2%93-%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A-%E8%8B%A5%E5%B1%AC%E5%AF%A6%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E5%AF%A6%E7%BF%92%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-130000347.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25B6%2581%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25B1%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25A4%2596%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%2599%2590%25E8%25B2%2593-%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A-%25E8%258B%25A5%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%25B5%2582%25E6%25AD%25A2%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E7%25BF%2592%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BD%259C-130000347.html&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEJmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=164432b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%89%E8%B6%81%E5%90%8C%E5%B1%8B%E4%B8%BB%E5%A4%96%E9%81%8A%E8%99%90%E8%B2%93-%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A-%E8%8B%A5%E5%B1%AC%E5%AF%A6%E7%B5%82%E6%AD%A2%E5%AF%A6%E7%BF%92%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C-130000347.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/z5wbcu5oL9Pc6zvvFEYojQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-05/c55b4990-6ba9-11e9-b9f7-8f15a02ecea5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fz5wbcu5oL9Pc6zvvFEYojQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-05%2Fc55b4990-6ba9-11e9-b9f7-8f15a02ecea5&h=8899b0bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港科大女生涉趁同屋主外遊虐貓 騰訊：若屬實終止實習工作<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】內地有網友在微博開名舉報其同屋合租人董怡萱，趁自己旅遊不在家期間虐待其愛貓，包括腳踢、毆打、追趕等。事主表示，上周四（25日）到泰國旅遊，出發時她委託董怡萱幫助照顧愛貓，對方亦答應。至上周六（27日）凌晨1、2時，她查看家中閉路電視時卻驚見董怡萱以各種方式虐待其愛貓。<br />\n<br />\n她隨即打電話給對方，但對方一直拒聽。她繼續翻查閉路電視，發現董怡萱不但踢踹、毆打其貓，「甚至提着牠的尾巴不放下來，聽着我的貓慘叫取樂3分半鐘之長」，又將貓關在貓沙盆內達10分鐘以上，甚至用枕頭塞住縫隙，令貓貓無法走出及呼吸。<br />\n<br />\n事主續指，董怡萱虐貓時不斷發出興奮、令人毛骨悚然的尖叫。雙方隨後就事件溝通，但董怡萱聲稱是貓在她牀上瀨尿才出手懲罰，態度毫無歉意，且明確表示「就是要打貓，報警隨便」的挑釁態度。<br />\n<br />\n事主其後報警處理，但她認為相關部門調解後，董怡萱依舊毫無愧疚，從未真誠道歉，因此決定在網上公開事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />畜牲真係無隻正常"},{"pid":"0b2c2bd9b23a65da5611ab7006d680b14b895909","tid":1133371,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a48e6998dfe85752beb2afe0f737b0bb20bb825","tid":1133371,"uid":30146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T14:33:12.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦仆街"},{"pid":"f01b0533b8b4478d8aa38173e4f4dfd37f10f6fb","tid":1133371,"uid":178301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T08:12:54.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n之前UST fb好多人comment屌<br />\n今日已經唔記得左了"}]}